N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 9 ยง 4814.12 - Time during which license is effective

State Regulations
A license as an authorized commercial lessor shall be
valid for a period not exceeding one year or until revoked or suspended by the
licensing authority or by the commission. Notes
